s</h5><p>In addition to other prohibitions as set forth in the Terms of Service, you are prohibited from using the site or its content for any unlawful purpose, to solicit others to perform or participate in any unlawful acts, or to violate any international or local regulations.</p><h5 class="mt-4 fw-bold text-uppercase">8. Governing Law</h5><p>These Terms of Service and any separate agreements whereby we provide you Services shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of India.</p><h5 class="mt-4 fw-bold text-uppercase">9. Contact Information</h5><p>Questions about the Terms of Service should be sent to us at <a href="mailto:grahasthee@gmail.com">grahasthee@gmail.com</a></p>'
